You are guaranteed to receive a prequalification decision from any of the lending services covered in this review. Simply click on the START NOW link to be transferred to a lending service where you can review the information and apply for a loan.

While lending decisions can be guaranteed, no personal or payday loan lender can guarantee instant loan approval. Your bad credit may hurt your chances for a short-term personal cash loan but should have no impact on your application for a payday loan.

If you can demonstrate that you’re currently employed and have sufficient income, it’s more than likely your payday cash advance request will be approved, although guaranteed approval loans don’t exist.

